5A1F4B4A.Line1.6D03F: I’m saying it’s impossible to know. She can peer into hearts. Tell us what we want to hear. You’ve seen it with Donan, Elias, and others.

F413C4CC.Line3.6D03F: To trust her would mean gambling with the fate of all humankind. Not a risk I’m willing to take.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “You’re saying she has plans beyond protecting humanity?”
